  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in China. This trial aims for a comparison of the effect on glycemic
      control in subjects with type 2 diabetes of insulin detemir or NPH-insulin given once daily
      at bedtime as add-on to oral anti-diabetic drug(s).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
